SELECT X.ORDER_DATE, X.DANUI, X.DANUI1, X.DRG_BUNHO, X.BUNHO, X.DV, X.DRG_GRP, X.NAME , X.GWA, X.BOGYONG_CODE, X.BOGYONG_NAME, X.NALSU, X.BUNRYU1, X.CAUTION_NM, X.JAERYO_NAME, X.GYUNBON_YN, SUM(X.SU), X.RP,X.HOPE_DATE, X.DONBOK FROM (SELECT B.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE , FN_DRG_LOAD_CODE_MENT ('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'1'), B.ORDER_DANUI), B.JAERYO_CODE) DANUI , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_GROUP_KEY('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'2'), B.ORDER_DANUI)) DANUI1 , B.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO , B.BUNHO BUNHO , B.DV DV , LTRIM(TO_CHAR(TO_NUMBER(MAX(A.DRG_GRP)),'990.9' )) DRG_GRP , FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO) NAME , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA, B.ORDER_DATE) GWA , A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE , FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE) BOGYONG_NAME , MAX(DECODE(FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) , 'Y', B.DV,B.NALSU)) NALSU , SUBSTRB(TRIM(B.BUNRYU1),1,1) BUNRYU1
, SUBSTRB(FN_DRG_LOAD_CAUTION_NM(A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O' )||CHR(10)|| TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_REMARK( A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O')) ,1,200)|| DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '4',CHR(10)|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA', B.JUSA_GUBUN)) CAUTION_NM
, ' ' JAERYO_NAME , NVL(B.GYUNBON_YN, 'N') GYUNBON_YN , SUM(1) SU , 'Rp'||A.SERIAL_V RP , FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', A.HOPE_DATE ) HOPE_DATE , FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) DONBOK FROM DRG2010 B , DRG2030 A WHERE B.ORDER_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_jubsu_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND B.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND B.BUNRYU1 IN ('1','3','8','9') AND B.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL
AND NVL(B.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' -- DC ??? AND NVL(B.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' -- ?? ??? AND NVL(B.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') <> 'Y' -- ?? ??E AND NVL(B.MIX_GROUP, 'N') = 'N' -- MIX_GROUP NULL AND B.FKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003 AND B.ORDER_DATE = A.JUBSU_DATE AND B.DRG_BUNHO = A.DRG_BUNHO GROUP BY B.ORDER_DATE , FN_DRG_LOAD_CODE_MENT ('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'1'), B.ORDER_DANUI), B.JAERYO_CODE) , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_GROUP_KEY('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE, '2'), B.ORDER_DANUI)) , B.DRG_BUNHO , B.BUNHO , B.DV , SUBSTRB(TRIM(B.BUNRYU1),1,1) , FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO) , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA, B.ORDER_DATE) , A.BOGYONG_CODE , FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE)
, SUBSTRB(FN_DRG_LOAD_CAUTION_NM(A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O' )||CHR(10)|| TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_REMARK( A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O')) ,1,200)|| DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '4',CHR(10)|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA', B.JUSA_GUBUN))
, NVL(B.GYUNBON_YN, 'N') , 'Rp'||A.SERIAL_V , FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', A.HOPE_DATE ) , FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) UNION ALL SELECT B.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE , FN_DRG_LOAD_CODE_MENT ('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'1'), B.ORDER_DANUI), B.JAERYO_CODE) DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_GROUP_KEY('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'2'), B.ORDER_DANUI)) DANUI1 ,B.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,B.BUNHO BUNHO ,B.DV DV ,LTRIM(TO_CHAR(TO_NUMBER(MAX(A.DRG_GRP)),'99990.9' )) DRG_GRP ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO) NAME ,FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA, B.ORDER_DATE) GWA ,A.BOGYONG_CODE BOGYONG_CODE ,FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE) BOGYONG_NAME ,MAX(DECODE(FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) , 'Y', B.DV,B.NALSU)) NALSU ,SUBSTRB(TRIM(B.BUNRYU1),1,1) BUNRYU1
,SUBSTRB(FN_DRG_LOAD_CAUTION_NM(A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O' )||CHR(10)|| TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_REMARK( A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O')) ,1,200)|| DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '4',CHR(10)|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA', B.JUSA_GUBUN)) CAUTION_NM
,' ' JAERYO_NAME ,NVL(B.GYUNBON_YN, 'N') GYUNBON_YN ,SUM(1) SU ,'Rp'||A.SERIAL_V RP ,FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', A.HOPE_DATE ) HOPE_DATE ,FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) DONBOK FROM DRG2010 B ,DRG2030 A WHERE B.ORDER_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_jubsu_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND B.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND B.BUNRYU1 IN ('1','3','8','9') AND B.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND NVL(B.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' -- DC ??? AND NVL(B.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' -- ?? ??? AND NVL(B.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') <> 'Y' -- ?? ??E AND NVL(B.MIX_GROUP, 'N') <> 'N' -- MIX_GROUP NULL AND B.FKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003 AND B.ORDER_DATE = A.JUBSU_DATE AND B.DRG_BUNHO = A.DRG_BUNHO GROUP BY B.ORDER_DATE , FN_DRG_LOAD_CODE_MENT ('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'1'), B.ORDER_DANUI), B.JAERYO_CODE) , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_GROUP_KEY('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE, '2'), B.ORDER_DANUI)) , B.DRG_BUNHO , B.BUNHO , B.DV , SUBSTRB(TRIM(B.BUNRYU1),1,1) , FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO) , FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA, B.ORDER_DATE) , A.BOGYONG_CODE , FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE)
, SUBSTRB(FN_DRG_LOAD_CAUTION_NM(A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O' )||CHR(10)|| TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_REMARK( A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O')) ,1,200)|| DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '4',CHR(10)|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA', B.JUSA_GUBUN))
, NVL(B.GYUNBON_YN, 'N') , 'Rp'||A.SERIAL_V , FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', A.HOPE_DATE ) , FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) UNION SELECT B.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,FN_DRG_LOAD_CODE_MENT ('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'1'), B.ORDER_DANUI), B.JAERYO_CODE) DANUI ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_GROUP_KEY('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'2'), B.ORDER_DANUI)) DANUI1 ,B.DRG_BUNHO ,B.BUNHO ,B.DV ,LTRIM(TO_CHAR(TO_NUMBER(MAX(A.DRG_GRP)),'99990.9' )) DRG_GRP ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO) NAME ,FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA, B.ORDER_DATE) GWA ,NVL(A.BOGYONG_CODE, 'XXX') BOGYONG_CODE
,TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_REMARK( A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O'))|| TRIM(DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '6', FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE),'') ) ,0 NALSU ,SUBSTRB(TRIM(B.BUNRYU1),1,1) BUNRYU1
,TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_CAUTION_NM(A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O' ))||CHR(10)|| DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '4',CHR(10)|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA', B.JUSA_GUBUN)) CAUTION_NM
,RPAD(TRIM(FN_INV_LOAD_JAERYO_NAME(B.JAERYO_CODE, '1')), 36)|| ' '|| CASE WHEN B.ORD_SURYANG >0 AND B.ORD_SURYANG < 1 THEN lTRIM(TO_CHAR(B.ORD_SURYANG, '0.9')) ELSE LTRIM(TO_CHAR(B.ORD_SURYANG)) END|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', B.ORDER_DANUI) JAERYO_CODE
,NVL(B.GYUNBON_YN, 'N') GYUNBON_YN ,0 SU ,'Rp'||A.SERIAL_V RP ,FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', A.HOPE_DATE ) HOPE_DATE ,FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) DONBOK FROM DRG2010 B ,DRG2030 A WHERE B.ORDER_DATE = TO_DATE(:f_jubsu_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND B.DRG_BUNHO = :f_drg_bunho AND B.BUNRYU1 IN ('4', '6') AND NVL(B.DC_YN,'N') = 'N' -- DC ??? AND NVL(B.BANNAB_YN,'N') = 'N' -- ?? ??? AND NVL(B.WONYOI_ORDER_YN,'N') <> 'Y' -- ?? ??E AND B.FKOCS1003 = A.FKOCS1003 AND B.ORDER_DATE = A.JUBSU_DATE AND B.DRG_BUNHO = A.DRG_BUNHO GROUP BY B.ORDER_DATE ,FN_DRG_LOAD_CODE_MENT ('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE,'1'), B.ORDER_DANUI), B.JAERYO_CODE) ,FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_GROUP_KEY('ORD_DANUI', NVL(FN_DRG_LABEL_DANUI(B.JAERYO_CODE, '2'), B.ORDER_DANUI)) ,B.DRG_BUNHO ,B.BUNHO ,B.DV ,SUBSTRB(TRIM(B.BUNRYU1),1,1) ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(B.BUNHO) ,FN_BAS_LOAD_GWA_NAME(B.GWA, B.ORDER_DATE) ,A.BOGYONG_CODE ,TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_REMARK( A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O'))|| TRIM(DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '6', FN_DRG_LOAD_BOGYONG_NAME(A.BOGYONG_CODE),'') )
,TRIM(FN_DRG_LOAD_CAUTION_NM(A.JUBSU_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, A.SERIAL_V, 'O' ))||CHR(10)|| DECODE(B.BUNRYU1, '4',CHR(10)|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('JUSA', B.JUSA_GUBUN))
,RPAD(TRIM(FN_INV_LOAD_JAERYO_NAME(B.JAERYO_CODE, '1')), 36)|| ' '|| CASE WHEN B.ORD_SURYANG >0 AND B.ORD_SURYANG < 1 THEN lTRIM(TO_CHAR(B.ORD_SURYANG, '0.9')) ELSE LTRIM(TO_CHAR(B.ORD_SURYANG)) END|| FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', B.ORDER_DANUI)
,NVL(B.GYUNBON_YN, 'N') ,'Rp'||A.SERIAL_V ,FN_BAS_TO_JAPAN_DATE_CONVERT('1', A.HOPE_DATE ) ,FN_DRG_LOAD_DONBOK_YN(A.BOGYONG_CODE) ) X GROUP BY X.ORDER_DATE, X.DANUI, X.DANUI1, X.DRG_BUNHO , X.BUNHO , X.DV , X.DRG_GRP, X.NAME , X.GWA , X.BOGYONG_CODE, X.BOGYONG_NAME, X.NALSU, X.BUNRYU1, X.CAUTION_NM, X.JAERYO_NAME, X.GYUNBON_YN, X.RP, X.HOPE_DATE, X.DONBOK ORDER BY 18

data.name: layAutoJubsu.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) SUNAME ,DECODE(NVL(A.BORYU_YN,'N'),'N',' ','Y') BORYU_YN ,MIN(C.ORDER_REMARK) ORDER_REMARK ,MIN(C.DRG_REMARK) DRG_REMARK FROM OUT1001 D ,DRG9041 C ,OCS1003 B ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.ORDER_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE(:f_from_date) AND TO_DATE(:f_to_date) AND A.GWA LIKE NVL(:f_gwa,'%') AND :f_bunho IS NULL AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN, 'N') = :f_wonyoi_yn AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'N') OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'Y') OR (:f_gubun = '3')) AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND C.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND A.FKOCS1003 = B.PKOCS1003 AND SUBSTR(B.ORDER_GUBUN,2,1) IN ('C','D') AND B.FKOUT1001 = D.PKOUT1001 AND D.NAEWON_YN = 'E' GROUP BY A.BUNHO, A.ORDER_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, DECODE(NVL(A.BORYU_YN,'N'),'N',' ','Y') UNION ALL SELECT A.BUNHO BUNHO ,A.ORDER_DATE ORDER_DATE ,A.DRG_BUNHO DRG_BUNHO ,FN_OUT_LOAD_SUNAME(A.BUNHO) SUNAME ,DECODE(NVL(A.BORYU_YN,'N'),'N',' ','Y') BORYU_YN ,MIN(C.ORDER_REMARK) ORDER_REMARK ,MIN(C.DRG_REMARK) DRG_REMARK FROM OUT1001 D ,DRG9041 C ,OCS1003 B ,DRG2010 A WHERE A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND NVL(A.WONYOI_ORDER_YN, 'N') = :f_wonyoi_yn AND ((:f_gubun = '1' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'N') OR (:f_gubun = '2' AND NVL(A.PRINT_YN,'N') = 'Y') OR (:f_gubun = '3')) AND NVL(A.DC_YN,'N') <> 'Y' AND A.SOURCE_FKOCS1003 IS NULL AND C.BUNHO (+)= A.BUNHO AND A.FKOCS1003 = B.PKOCS1003 AND SUBSTR(B.ORDER_GUBUN,2,1) IN ('C','D') AND B.FKOUT1001 = D.PKOUT1001 AND D.NAEWON_YN = 'E' GROUP BY A.BUNHO, A.ORDER_DATE, A.DRG_BUNHO, DECODE(NVL(A.BORYU_YN,'N'),'N',' ','Y') ORDER BY 2 DESC, 3 DESC
